		<description><![CDATA[<p>最近見つけたGoogle Chromeの拡張機能でGoogle Readerの画面を３カラムにして綺麗にしてくれます。 3 Column Reader 先ほどのページのDownloadを押してReaderにアクセスするだ [&#8230;]</p>
<p>投稿<a rel="nofollow" href="/diary/3-column-reader/">3 Column Readerがおすすめ</a>は<a rel="nofollow" href="/">colopixie</a>の最初に登場しました。</p>
]]></description>
				<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><img src="https://i1.wp.com/colopixie.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/09/google_reader.png?resize=558%2C180" alt="" title="google_reader" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-93" srcset="https://i1.wp.com/colopixie.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/09/google_reader.png?w=558&amp;ssl=1 558w, https://i1.wp.com/colopixie.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/09/google_reader.png?resize=300%2C96&amp;ssl=1 300w" sizes="(max-width: 558px) 100vw, 558px" data-recalc-dims="1" /><br />
最近見つけたGoogle Chromeの拡張機能でGoogle Readerの画面を３カラムにして綺麗にしてくれます。<br />
<a href="http://zackarycorbett.com/3columnreader/" target="_blank">3 Column Reader<br />
<img src="https://i2.wp.com/colopixie.com/wp-content/themes/colopixie/images/download.png" alt="Download" class="sampleview" data-recalc-dims="1"></a></p>
<p>先ほどのページのDownloadを押してReaderにアクセスするだけなのですが、<br />
.co.jpのReaderページだと下のようになってしまうので<br />
<a href="https://i2.wp.com/colopixie.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/09/reader_big2.png" rel="lightbox[92]" title="reader_big2"><img src="https://i2.wp.com/colopixie.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/09/reader_big2-300x191.png?resize=300%2C191" alt="" title="reader_big2" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-95" srcset="https://i2.wp.com/colopixie.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/09/reader_big2.png?resize=300%2C191&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i2.wp.com/colopixie.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/09/reader_big2.png?resize=1024%2C653&amp;ssl=1 1024w, https://i2.wp.com/colopixie.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/09/reader_big2.png?w=1294&amp;ssl=1 1294w" sizes="(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px" data-recalc-dims="1" /></a></p>
<p><a href="http://www.google.com/reader/view/" target="_blank">http://www.google.com/reader/view/</a><br />
にアクセスすると適用されます。<br />
<a href="https://i1.wp.com/colopixie.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/09/reader_big1.png" rel="lightbox[92]" title="reader_big1"><img src="https://i1.wp.com/colopixie.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/09/reader_big1-300x191.png?resize=300%2C191" alt="" title="reader_big1" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-94" srcset="https://i1.wp.com/colopixie.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/09/reader_big1.png?resize=300%2C191&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i1.wp.com/colopixie.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/09/reader_big1.png?resize=1024%2C653&amp;ssl=1 1024w, https://i1.wp.com/colopixie.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/09/reader_big1.png?w=1294&amp;ssl=1 1294w" sizes="(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px" data-recalc-dims="1" /></a></p>
<p>３カラムにするには、左上のメニューの≡を押せば３カラムになります。</p>
<p>ぜひWebでGoogle Readerをお使いの方は入れてみてはどうでしょうか。</p>
<p>投稿<a rel="nofollow" href="/diary/3-column-reader/">3 Column Readerがおすすめ</a>は<a rel="nofollow" href="/">colopixie</a>の最初に登場しました。</p>
]]></content:encoded>
